Corey's Analysis Slide:
Next I mapped the democracy index in Sur, Mexico by state.
```{r}
df2<- df |>
  select( 
    country_name,
    state_name,
    region_name,
    year,
    SUR_index_sub_exe
  ) |> 
  mutate(Democracy = SUR_index_sub_exe) |>
  filter(country_name == 'MEXICO', region_name == 'SUR' )

plot1 <- df2 |>
  ggplot(aes(x = year, y = Democracy))+
  geom_line(aes(colour = state_name)) +
  labs(
    title = 'Democracy in Sur, Mexico by State',
    x = 'Democracy Score',
    y = 'Year',
    legend = 'State name'
  ) +
  theme(
    panel.grid.major = element_line(color = 'lightgrey'),
    panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
    panel.background = element_rect(fill = 'white'),
    title = element_text(face = 'bold', size = 12))
plot1
```